edu.stanford.smi.protege.util
Class Assert

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--edu.stanford.smi.protege.util.Assert
public class Assert
extends Object

A utility class for checking assertions. Assertion failures throw AssertionFailedError. Every method throws the error directly so that only one Assert class method shows up on the stack trace. Modeled on the JUnit Assert class.

Author:
Ray Fergerson (fergerson@smi.stanford.edu)
